oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mary Lou Turner at the Franklin Senior High School
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Turner, Mary Lou; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) announcing a show with the all star cast from the world famous WWVA Jamboree featuring Mary Lou Turner and the Ned Davis Show with Sue McKim at the Franklin Senior High School on September 20. Poster features a metal photoplate of Mary Lou Turner.
